'''Champion Squadron''' was one of the three [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wing]] [[Squadron/Legends|squadrons]] that made up [[Defender Wing]]. The other two were [[Guardian Squadron|Guardian]] and [[Warden Squadron|Warden]] Squadrons. Its [[Pilot/Legends|pilots]] liked to play [[slingball]].

